dc_title_s: South Pacific Ocean, South America, Chile, Boca del Guafo to Golfo de Penas (Raster Image)
dc_description_s: Prepared and published by the National Imagery and Mapping Agency. Depths shown by isolines and soundings. Relief shown by hachures and spot heights. "From a Chilean chart of 1978." "Copyright 1997 by the United States Government. No copyright claimed under Title 17 U.S.C." "Soundings in meters." Includes index to next larger scale charts. Map no.22370. This map is part of a collection of scanned and georeferenced nautical charts produced by the National Geospatial-Intelligence Agency (NGA).
dc_creator_sm: United States. National Imagery and Mapping Agency
